   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2430, recto: (1) I, Daniel, (2) he writes to Koloje, (3) he owes (4) her one artaba (5) of dates or one ho of wheat, (6) which I shall give to you in Thoth (7) of the fifteenth (year).  (8) I, Daniel, assent (9) to this sherd which I have (10) written on the twenty-sixth (11) of Epep, (12) under Manasseh.</ab>
         </div>
